{"tid":2132384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國將就TikTok是否影響國家安全提交建議","createTime":"2020-07-30T10:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T10:54:18.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f302ec13395a1b22b7f762fc9b747c49bee40c30","tid":2132384,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"姆努欽對記者表示，由財政部領導的美國海外投資委員會，正對TikTok進行審查，會在本周內向總統提交建議。<br />\n<br />\n今次是美國政府首次承認對TikTok進行審查，較早前傳媒報道，美國對TikTok母公司北京字節跳動，以10億美元收購一個社交應用程式進行調查，如果美國海外投資委員會認為有關收購影響美國國家安全，可以勒令取消交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=399817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399817&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0ef1588b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399817&h=35545019\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=399817</a>"},{"pid":"e58b48c30648faf76bba4c5bae2b3e6c82f13ffc","tid":2132384,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"142b4c5ddfc5d6f9100b617c5ca6551eb4f70f22","tid":2132384,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}